</page>
<page title="Style sheets" subsection="">
<layer name="alpha"/>
<view layers="alpha" active="alpha"/>
<text layer="alpha" pin="h" transformations="translations" pos="0 770" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="1680" height="255.986" depth="229.075" valign="top" style="itemize">\item IPE has style sheets. Think of them like a CSS file. \\Technically, they&apos;re XML.
\item Primarily, the style sheets define all of the \ul{property options} you have for your objects (e.g. colors, line widths, text sizes etc.)
\item They can also control the \ul{appearance} of your page(s), including possible \ul{templates} like the one used in this presentation
\item They can define a set of \LaTeX \ \ul{packages} you always need</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 0 25.671" pin="h" transformations="translations" pos="0 252.939" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="1680" height="149.297" depth="122.1" valign="top" style="itemize">\item Basically, style sheets can do a lot and are advanced IPE stuff
\item If you want to check or \ul{edit} your/this/any document&apos;s style sheets, press \textcolor{kn_seegruen}{Ctrl+Shift+S} for options
\item \textcolor{kn_seegruen}{Ctrl+Shift+U} updates them if you made and saved changes</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 20.3068 3.13072" transformations="translations" pos="828.62 95.8883" stroke="kn_karpfenblau" type="label" width="793.029" height="20.0475" depth="5.83" valign="baseline" size="tiny">(more on how style sheets work in the official IPE documentation)</text>
</page>
<page section="Making presentations in IPE">
<layer name="alpha"/>
<view layers="alpha" active="alpha"/>
<text layer="alpha" matrix="1 0 0 1 0 -352" pin="h" transformations="translations" pos="0 770" stroke="kn_seeblau" type="minipage" width="1680" height="58.399" depth="31.075" valign="top" size="LARGE">Making presentations in IPE</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 -242.98 4.12059" transformations="translations" pos="430.983 254.531" stroke="kn_grau" type="label" width="839.443" height="32.0375" depth="9.735" valign="baseline" size="footnote">(This is what you&apos;re here for anyway, right?)</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 -24.5891 -80.3511" transformations="translations" pos="430.983 254.531" stroke="kn_grau" type="label" width="1266.52" height="32.0375" depth="9.735" valign="baseline" size="footnote">(But don&apos;t sleep on IPE&apos;s potential to make figures for your thesis)</text>
</page>
<page title="Presentation concepts: Page, layer, view" subsection="">
<layer name="alpha"/>
<layer name="beta"/>
<layer name="gamma"/>
<layer name="delta"/>
<layer name="epsilon"/>
<view layers="alpha" active="alpha"/>
<view layers="beta gamma" active="beta"/>
<view layers="beta delta" active="gamma"/>
<view layers="beta epsilon" active="epsilon"/>
<text layer="alpha" pin="h" transformations="translations" pos="0 770" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="1680" height="143.594" depth="116.38" valign="top" style="itemize">\item A presentation made with IPE is simply a set of \ul{PDF slides}. This means no fancy transitions, just plain content.
\item IPE lets you create \emph{pages, views, and layers}. Here&apos;s how they translate to your final presentation:</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 0 -12.3334" pin="h" transformations="translations" pos="0 478.026" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="1680" height="239.679" depth="212.795" valign="top" size="small" style="itemize">\item Each \emph{page} in IPE is a new piece of canvas for you to draw on.
\item Each \emph{view} in IPE will be a \ul{new slide} in your final PDF. Each IPE page may have multiple views.
\item IPE&apos;s \emph{layers} allow you to group objects and manage their visibility. Whether a layer appears on a slide is determined by whether it is part of the corresponding view. New objects get added to the \emph{active layer} (yellow highlighting).</text>
<text layer="beta" pin="h" transformations="translations" pos="0 770" stroke="black" type="minipage" width="1680" height="39.6" depth="12.21" valign="top" style="item">Consider this structure for example:</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 -67.3812 72.9665" transformations="translations" pos="194.556 580.611" stroke="black" type="label" width="125.752" height="39.6275" depth="12.155" valign="baseline">Page</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 -85.8811 -96.1927" transformations="translations" pos="213.056 434.667" stroke="black" type="label" width="117.645" height="39.611" depth="0.88" valign="baseline">View</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 -110.548 303.7" transformations="translations" pos="237.722 192.111" stroke="black" type="label" width="134.299" height="39.6" depth="11.715" valign="baseline">Layer</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 8.67431 34.5116" transformations="translations" pos="550.167 613.5" stroke="black" type="label" width="30.4645" height="38.6045" depth="0" valign="baseline">1</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 378.645 59.1783" transformations="translations" pos="877 588.833" stroke="black" type="label" width="30.4645" height="38.6045" depth="0" valign="baseline">2</text>
<group matrix="1 0 0 1 -5.76879 65.7673">
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 -55.5 149.544" transformations="translations" pos="490.556 280.5" stroke="black" type="label" width="134.024" height="39.6275" depth="11.385" valign="baseline">alpha</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 -141.833 192.711" transformations="translations" pos="759.833 237.333" stroke="black" type="label" width="106.629" height="39.611" depth="0.88" valign="baseline">beta</text>
</group>
<group matrix="1 0 0 1 95.0077 65.7673">
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 172.892 176.266" transformations="translations" pos="1002.39 253.778" stroke="black" type="label" width="182.683" height="29.7055" depth="12.155" valign="baseline">gamma</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 324.777 149.544" transformations="translations" pos="490.556 280.5" stroke="black" type="label" width="134.024" height="39.6275" depth="11.385" valign="baseline">alpha</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 249.172 192.711" transformations="translations" pos="759.833 237.333" stroke="black" type="label" width="106.629" height="39.611" depth="0.88" valign="baseline">beta</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 37 -10.7894" transformations="translations" pos="1380.61 440.833" stroke="black" type="label" width="118.794" height="39.611" depth="0.88" valign="baseline">delta</text>
</group>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 378.645 59.1783" transformations="translations" pos="877 588.833" stroke="black" type="label" width="30.4645" height="38.6045" depth="0" valign="baseline">2</text>
<group matrix="1 0 0 1 95.0077 65.7673">
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 172.892 176.266" transformations="translations" pos="1002.39 253.778" stroke="black" type="label" width="182.683" height="29.7055" depth="12.155" valign="baseline">gamma</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 324.777 149.544" transformations="translations" pos="490.556 280.5" stroke="black" type="label" width="134.024" height="39.6275" depth="11.385" valign="baseline">alpha</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 249.172 192.711" transformations="translations" pos="759.833 237.333" stroke="black" type="label" width="106.629" height="39.611" depth="0.88" valign="baseline">beta</text>
<text matrix="1 0 0 1 37 -10.7894" transformations="translations" pos="1380.61 440.833" stroke="black" type="label" width="118.794" height="39.611" depth="0.88" valign="baseline">delta</text>
</group>
